Time at Computer Sciences Corp

























                                                The largest number of Computer Sciences Corp employees graduated from River High  School, Thames Valley State Technical College, and THE CHUBB INSTITUTE.
                                            

                                                For further insight into Computer Sciences Corp's intellectual environment, look at the trends in employee education. In terms of educational backgrounds at Computer Sciences Corp, the most common among employees is high school graduate (10% of workers). In terms of academic achievement at Computer Sciences Corp, about 5.71% of employees hold a Bachelor of Arts degree while 7.14% have a Bachelor of Science.
                                            

                                                Applicants seeking opportunities at Computer Sciences Corp have also shown interest in Computer Sciences Corporation, Universal Solutions International Inc, Brown Corp of Moberly Missouri, Rockwell Automation, and Safe auto Insurance co.
                                            



























