3 Computer Sciences Corp Senior Product Specialist Salaries 

Browse Computer Sciences Corp Salaries by Job Title →

Computer Sciences Corp Senior Product Specialists earn $117,000 annually, or $56 per hour, which is 63% higher than the national average for all Senior Product Specialists at $61,000 annually and 63% higher than the national salary average for ​all working Americans. The highest paid Senior Product Specialists work for Teradyne at $138,000 annually and the lowest paid Senior Product Specialists work for DirectBuy at $27,000 annually.






