                                            SolutionsCloud Applications (Oracle Cloud Marketplace)Petroleum Enterprise IntelligenceThis application has been designated as ready to run on the Oracle Cloud Platform based on the application's support of the Oracle Cloud compatible technology products and operating systems.Enterprise Intelligence for RetailCSC's Enterprise Intelligence for Retail (EIR) is a business intelligence solution designed specifically for the retail industry, providing role-based decision support for retailers.ENTERPRISE MANAGERA fully integrated, single database, end-to-end healthcare solution, Enterprise Management can be scaled for large healthcare enterprises/providers.Oracle Exastack OptimizedPetroleum Enterprise Intelligence  CSC’s Petroleum Enterprise Intelligence (PEI) solution is a business analytics solutions using Oracle Business Intelligence that integrates data from financial, technical and operational systems and data stores. Its primary functions are visualization, consolidation, management and analysis of data across an upstream business process used in exploration and production. Used for visualization and reporting, PEI enables specialized portals to be built that blend business, process, location and people intelligence for the critical task of finding, producing and maintaining the flow of hydrocarbons.Designed for global and domestic oil and gas C-level executives and business line management, PEI provides a flexible solution to solve business issues of integrating, comprehending and evaluating the wide variety and amount of data needed for fast, accurate decision making to optimize operations. This application has achieved:   Oracle Exadata Optimized, Oracle Exalogic OptimizedOracle Exastack ReadyPetroleum Enterprise Intelligence CSC’s Petroleum Enterprise Intelligence (PEI) solution is a business analytics solutions using Oracle Business Intelligence that integrates data from financial, technical and operational systems and data stores. Its primary functions are visualization, consolidation, management and analysis of data across an upstream business process used in exploration and production. Used for visualization and reporting, PEI enables specialized portals to be built that blend business, process, location and people intelligence for the critical task of finding, producing and maintaining the flow of hydrocarbons.Designed for global and domestic oil and gas C-level executives and business line management, PEI provides a flexible solution to solve business issues of integrating, comprehending and evaluating the wide variety and amount of data needed for fast, accurate decision making to optimize operations.This application has achieved:   Oracle Exadata Ready, Oracle Exalogic Ready, Oracle Database Ready, Oracle WebLogic Ready, Oracle Linux Ready, Oracle SuperCluster ReadyEnterprise Intelligence for RetailCSC's Enterprise Intelligence for Retail (EIR) is a business intelligence solution designed specifically for the retail industry, providing role-based decision support for retailers.This application has achieved:   Oracle Database Ready, Oracle WebLogic Ready, Oracle Linux Ready, Oracle Exadata Ready, Oracle Exalogic Ready, Oracle SuperCluster ReadyFixed Scope OfferingsEnterprise Intelligence for RetailCSC's Enterprise Intelligence for Retail (EIR) is a business intelligence solution designed specifically for the retail industry, providing role-based decision support for retailers.Cloud Fixed Scope Offerings:   Oracle Financials CloudOn-Premise SolutionsAccelerated Value RealizationACCELERATED VALUE REALIZATION (AVR) - CSC’s experience, passion for results, transformational approach and understanding experience help you 
